  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ICharacterReferrer, ICharacterTag, ITag

    public class DefineShape4Tag
extends DefineShape3Tag
    Represents a DefineShape4 tag in a SWF file.

    DefineShape4 extends the capabilities of DefineShape3Tag by using a new line style record in the shape. LINESTYLE2 allows new types of joins and caps as well as scaling options and the ability to fill a stroke.
